    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Huic etiam abbati <persName ref="#people/316" key="#Count">Lando</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> filius <persName ref="#people/156"
                            key="#Princeps">Landolfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs> obtulit <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84">Beato Benedicto</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Lakes">lacu Iuliani</rs> que esse videtur in <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/2000">Vicu Albu</placeName>,
                        integra ipsa <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> que esse videtur infra
                        has <rs key="#Confinia">fines</rs>, sicut incipit a capite de <rs
                            key="#Mountains">Monte de Albetu</rs> et quomodo decurrit fine <rs
                            key="#Confinia">pesclu</rs> qui se nominat <rs key="#Confinia">de
                            Dominicu</rs> et quomodo pergit in <rs key="#Confinia">Sancto Vito</rs>
                        et vadit ad <rs key="#Confinia #Mountains">colle monacisco qui Broccu</rs>
                        vocatur et quomodo mergit in ipsa <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, de alia
                        parte quomodo vadit ipsa via publica da ipsu <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Bridges/pontoons">ponte da Pini</rs>,<rs
                            key="#Confinia #Natural_landscape"> fine ubi dicitur Cerru Aureu</rs>,
                        et in tertia parte fine <rs key="#Lakes">lacu Taurini</rs>, da quarta parte
                        fine supascripto monte de Albetu. Infra has fines et indicationes, simul cum
                        ipsu <rs>ribu qui se nominat Carpello</rs>, cum ripis et viis suis intrandi
                        et exiendi et cum omnia inferiora ac superiora sua, cunctum et integrum ipsa
                        iudicavi atque offerui in supradicto <rs key="#Monasteries">cenobio</rs>
                        Sancti Benedicti ad possessionem habendum et retinendum ad eius abbatibus et
                        rectoribus. Ego qui supradictus Lando comes et meis heredibus componere
                        obligamus ad partem iam dicti monasterii et ad eius abbatibus et rectoribus,
                        et omnia supradicta ego et heredes meos percompleamus ad parte ipsius
                        monasterii et ad eius abbatibus et rectoribus in suprascripta ratione. Et
                        hanc <rs key="#Cartula">cartam</rs> mee iudicationis atque offersionis de
                        qualiter continet firma permaneat in perpetuum. Et taliter ego qui
                        supradictus Lando comes pro remedium anime meae feci, et te <persName
                            key="#Notary"><name ref="Radipertus">Radipertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scribere rogavi. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capua</placeName>. Ego <persName
                            key="#Judge"><name ref="Adelmundus">Adelmundus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Adaldus"
                                >Adoaldus</name></persName> Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Audo">Audo</name></persName> Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gausus">Gautio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Penalty">Pena quinquaginta Bizantei solidi</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
